node.text: All I actually need is the power the nature 👐🏾 ⛰

SIIIIIIII ⚽️ 😂 @cristiano 

-HIIT WORKOUT -

The Focus is more on the abs 
  If you want to burn at least 300 calories in 20 mins and get a great pump than this is the Perfect workout for you 🔥. The focus is more on the abs but at the same time you burn really good and you get a better condition !
I currently do a lot of similar workouts to become more shredded 💪🏾

30 sec Action 
20 sec rest 

FEEL FREE TO SAVE 

If you need more help click the link in my bio and register so I can contact you to talk about you and your goals !💪🏾👊🏾

#hiitworkout #hiit #abs #upperbodyworkout #legs #shape #shredded #workhard #keepfighting

👉🏾CHEST WORKOUT 👈🏾

SAVE FOR LATER 🤙🏾

Thanks god I can train again 🙏🏾. Today I had a killer chest session .I am trying to be more creative with my training  and of course I train very careful. Feel free to increase the weight if you can . Today’s exercises are absolute destroyers . Give them a try 🤙🏾

🌪Incline triangle press  4x 20-15
🌪Stacked plate press.  4x 15-12
🌪Incline circle fly.  4x 15-12
🌪Flat dumbbell alternating bench press 4x 15-12
🌪Flat Dumbell Bench press 4x 15-12

Let’s go !

#chestday #chestworkout #chestgains #chesttraining #chestexercises

👉🏾Shoulder Session 👈🏾

SAVE FOR LATER 🔥 

My right arm is unfortunately still not really healthy, that’s why i can't train with much weight . Much weight is also not always important . You can stimulate the muscles in other ways. Today a few shoulder exercises that are extremely effective and help your delts to grow 💪🏾

4 x 15-12
30-40 sec rest between the sets 

Give them a try🤙🏾

#shoulderworkout #shoulders #shouldertraining #delts #homeworkout #workoutexercises

node.text:
Time to burn 🔥 

SAVE FOR LATER 🤙🏾
Turn on my post notifications 🔔

the best workouts I can recommend to anyone to burn good calories and at the same time pump up the muscles. if you don't like to use treadmill or stairmaster, these exercises are just perfect for you. I personally do 2 sessions every week and soon want to increase to 3 because the results I have achieved with those workouts are insane.

6 rounds 
30 sec action 
30 sec rest

Let’s go !

#hiitworkout #hiitcardio #hiittraining

node.text:
Anzeige *Auf dem Weg zurück zur alten Form unterstützen mich die Supplements von @officialbodylab24 enorm 🙌🏾. So eine gute Qualität hatte ich bisher noch nie.
Das Whey Protein gibts in über 20 geilen Geschmacksrichtungen zum Hammerpreis von nur 25€ für den 2-Kilo Eimer 😍
Hol dir schnell deine Lieblingssorte .link in der bio 👆🏾
Und für alle anderen Produkte gilt : mit (AMIN33 )33% Rabatt sichern 🤙🏾

#bodylap24 #bdlb24crew #officialbodylap24 #comeback #workhard #stayfocus #makeithappen

👉🏾Back day 👈🏾

Save for later 💪🏾
Turn on my post notifications 🔔 

After my arm injury i was able to do everything again step by step except back training . This is now my first back training after the surgery . i am thankful to be able to train my back again🙏🏾, but to reach my old shape I need to work a little bit harder 🙂

4 x 15-12 each exercise 

#backday #backworkout #backgains

node.text: Can you please pick me up ? 🤓👍🏾

One of my favorite hiit Workouts .it helps you burn good calories, improves your endurance and at the same time you become more athletic. 
Attention ⚠️ Through  such exercises you will not become a muscle beast :) 
Workouts you can combine with your bodybuilding split .

6 rounds 
30 sec Action 
30 sec Rest 

Save and give it a try 💪🏾

#hiitworkout #hiitcardio #hiittraining

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by AMIN ELKACH | ONLINE COACH in World Gym Cologne. May be an image of 1 person, biceps, standing and indoor.

node.text: Life is always ups or downs but this year was one of my worst. The cause was an injury 13 weeks ago on my right arm. I had to have a surgery and immediately after that I started counting the days until my recovery. Every day felt like a month. I wanted to quickly start doing what I enjoy most (my sport) again. Today I am abnormally grateful that I can train again without restrictions and above all that I am making progress towards my old shape every week. Appreciate what you have and be grateful !
